            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Jarvis 0.7.1</h2>
<p><b>Stability fix.</b> Resolves a crash that could occur right after updating the
app (a race in the Telegram engine during the brief overlap between the old and
new app instance).</p>
<ul>
  <li>The Telegram engine now starts its update listener only when it's actually
      needed, eliminating a startup race.</li>
  <li>Jarvis now ensures only one copy of the app runs at a time — a second
      launch hands over to the running one.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
